title: Max marvels at LeBron consistently hitting 3-pointers | First Take
author: NBA on ESPN
description:
Stephen A. Smith and Max Kellerman debate what message LeBron James sent after defeating reigning NBA MVP Giannis Antetokounmpo and the Milwaukee Bucks.
